<br>
Although Aly had other daughters whom she loved equally as Belle, they all had their other places in the world and Aly wouldn't dream of taking them from that.<br>
<br>
Belle however was an amazon and she had a place there. She had a family and a home now. All that was left was the coronation.<br>
<br>
Alysia stood in the sweat hut helping Belle prepare for the ritual. &quot;Don't forget everything I taught you as of lately. And remember, it's not a test, just an introduction to the tribe, to make things official.&quot;<br>
<br>
She took Belle's blonde hair in her hands as she braided the sides pinning them together with sacred amazon feathers. <br>
<br>
&quot;The Amazons might be a little stand off for the first little while, but there are those few that extend immediate blessings to fellow athelfi.&quot; She smiled as she took a piece of leather string and tied Belle's braids together in the back.<br>
<br>
&quot;Did you remember to set out your outfit for today?&quot;<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> AmazonBelle</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(5/11/01 8:32:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1> Belle sighed, nodding in responce to Aly's question.<br>
<br>
&quot;If it's not a test then why do I have to remember everything? You know I have a horrible memory.&quot;<br>
<br>
She pulled on her braid slightly, as she often did when she was nervous. She had become an initiate and a princess all in the same week...<br>
<br>
She bit her lower lip nervously, eyes darting about the room. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#993300>(5/11/01 11:30:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1> Aly smiled as she walked over to a section of the hut where she kept her own hair pieces as she began to pull her own hair up.<br>
<br>
&quot;Just words of wisdom sweetie.&quot;<br>
<br>
She walked over to her cleansing table and ran her hands through the smoke of some inscense burning near the water. She dipped her hands into the cold water and brought them to her face as she tried to cool herself down a bit. Alot had happened that week and for some reason, she herself was nervous.<br>
<br>
&quot;The tribe will love you darling.&quot; She smiled as she padded a dry cloth over her wet face looking at Belle.<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;I never thought I'd actually be preparing one of my daughters for a ritual like this.&quot; She smiled as she walked over to Belle pinning some Scynthian ritual beads to her top.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm very proud of you Belle.&quot;<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> AmazonBelle</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(5/12/01 11:39:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1> Belle smiled a little, glancing up at Aly..<br>
<br>
&quot;Are you going to be okay?&quot;<br>
<br>
She asked, unable to really keep her mind on the coronation anymore. She knew Aly had had an extremely hard week, but she didn't know what she could do to help...<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 75<br> <font color=#993300>(5/12/01 11:47:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1> Aly looked to her and smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm fine Belle. I've survived much worse than a bad week.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then took a ceremonial dagger and placed it in Belle's boots. She then walked over to where she had a medium sized staff and she placed a wolf medallion at the top of it and smoothed her hand over the wolf fure wrapped around the top. She sighed as she took a small feather attached to some beads and wrapped them around the top of the staff.<br>
<br>
&quot;You almost ready Belle?&quot;<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> AmazonBelle</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(5/12/01 11:52:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1> Belle took a deep breath and nodded slowly.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yeah, I guess...&quot;<br>
<br>
She reluctantly stood from her seat and walked over towards Aly, still biting her bottom lip nervously. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 76<br> <font color=#993300>(5/12/01 12:00:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1> Alysia nodded knowing how nervous she must be.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'll give you a moment to yourself to calm down a bit. Perhaps you can take this time to make peace with the Ancients.&quot; She smiled and took the staff in her hands and held it out to Belle.<br>
<br>
&quot;I made this for you last night. It's a ceremonial staff. Not used to fighting, but for the symbol of your place here.&quot; She smiled once again and handed the staff to Belle.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'll see you in a little bit.&quot;<br>
<br>
She then walked out the door of the hut. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> AmazonBelle</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(5/12/01 12:12:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1> Belle smiled a little, looking at the staff in her hand. <br>
<br>
After a moment or two of silently making piece with her mother, she glanced at a bracelet on her wrist. She'd been told it was an Amazon bracelet, and it'd be found on her wrist the day she was brought to Rome as an infant, so she could only assume it was from her mother.<br>
<br>
&quot;I won't forget you...&quot; <br>
<br>
She spoke quietly, then tilted her head back up. She slowly walk out of the sweathut and glanced to Aly.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm ready.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udawnithinia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dawnithinia </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Amazon Queen</span><br>  Posts: 83<br> <font color=#993300>(5/12/01 1:45:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=134.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=AmazonWarMaskofDeath WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coronation of Princess Belle</span><hr size=1>  Dawn had settled in a tree over looking most of Scynthia (sp?), it had been the same tree she fell to rest in during the Roman war. For once the remembrence of the war made Dawn's spine tingle and bring goosebumps to her arm. She growled thinking to herself &quot;Don't be so dumb Dawn. The Amazons didn't loose.&quot; Dawn shook her head lightly, as emerald eyes looked downward, watching Alysia and Belle. Dawn had yet to meet this intiate, well...no longer intiate Princess. Dawn shook her head, wasn't that a bit quick?<br>
