<br>
&quot;Cora was raised in Rome. In fact, that is where she lives now. She was a wonderful princess. My daughter Aliya, was born in Rome. She is the Healer of this tribe. I myself lived in Rome and continue to go there to see my grandchildren.&quot;<br>
<br>
She stepped forward holding her head high.<br>
<br>
&quot;And who's to say she won't lead this tribe to Victory? We don't need to be lead Dawn. Our battle is over for now. She is my daughter, and riteful heir in this tribe. She has amazon blood. And has the spirit of a true leader. The Ancients have told me so.&quot;<br>
<br>
She looked back to Belle and smiled.<br>
<br>
&quot;We are blind to the future, we have two choices. One, to either question everyone and eliminate those we do not know or trust. Or two, we can teach those who do not know, learn from them as sisters do.&quot; <br>
<br>
